53  void MYWE::execute(Dvector& Corr, Dvector& AR) { /*initialite*/
54 
55  mA(1, 1) = -Corr(mIQ + 1) / Corr(mIQ);
56  mB(1, 1) = -Corr(mIQ - 1) / Corr(mIQ);
57 
58  mRho(1) = (1.0 - mA(1, 1) * mB(1, 1)) * Corr(mIQ);
59 
60  /*recursion*/
61  for (unsigned k = 2; k <= mIP; k++) {
62  double sumA = 0.0;
63 
64  for (unsigned int l = 1; l < k; l++)
65  sumA += mA(k - 1, l) * Corr(mIQ + k - l);
66 
67  mA(k, k) = -(Corr(mIQ + k) + sumA) / mRho(k - 1);
68 
69  for (unsigned int i = 1; i < k; i++)
70  mA(k, i) = mA(k - 1, i) + mA(k, k) * mB(k - 1, k - i);
71 
72  double sumB = 0.0;
73 
74  for (unsigned int l = 1; l < k; l++)
75  sumB += mB(k - 1, l) * Corr(mIQ - k - l);
76 
77  mB(k, k) = -(Corr(mIQ - k) + sumB) / mRho(k - 1);
78 
79  for (unsigned int i = 1; i < k; i++)
80  mB(k, i) = mB(k - 1, i) + mB(k, k) * mA(k - 1, k - i);
81 
82  mRho(k) = (1.0 - mA(k, k) * mB(k, k)) * mRho(k - 1);
83  }
84 
85  for (unsigned int k = 1; k <= mIP; k++)
86  AR(k) = mA(mIP, k);
87 
88  AR(0) = 1.0;
89  };
90 }
